To create a new empty project.
# Setup env
## open platformio Home
## select `New project` -> `Node MCU 1.0` -> `Anrdoid` -> specify location

## explore files in the directory


## plug device into USB & USB into your laptop


## upload firmware on devide:
    * click on PlatformIO icon (left side)
    * `Build` & check results on terminal
    * `Upload`:
        * error `PermissionError: [Errno 13] Permission denied: '/dev/ttyUSB0`
        * fix: https://askubuntu.com/a/210230/778247 & 'newgrp dialout' & reboot

## Add prints into the loop
## Add default LED control
## Modify LED logic

